issue.title: View data can be larger than selected scope for data
issue.body:
It is possible for part of the pie chart to contain more time than the actual scope of the pie chart.

IE: I saw within the 10 minute scope that www.google.com was at 11 minutes in total

issue.title: Feature/better collection
issue.body:
- Fix issue of continuing to record when on another window.
  - Now polls and checks if window is active (3 seconds) and on first change of states, will store data
- Fix issue of continuing to record when computer is asleep
  - Now will store when computer is entering sleep state.
  - Won't store if computer was idle and entered sleep state.
- Fix issue of not updating the URL and Time when difference is too low
- Fix issue of not storing data correctly when given undefined URL.
  - Better handling of undefined URL and differentiating between an already existing website and a new one
- Comment code, explaining logic behind if statements
- Remove filter on chrome:// pages 
- Add helper functions to improve code clarity 
- Remove unused code

TL;DR A lot was done to improve the collection of data
